<header class="page-header">
  <h1>API key created</h1>
  <nav class="page-nav"><a href="/profile/api-keys">Back to API keys</a></nav>
</header>

<div class="flash flash-info">
  <p><strong>Copy your key NOW. It will not be shown again.</strong></p>
</div>

<dl class="api-key-detail">
  <dt>Name</dt><dd>{{keyName}}</dd>
  <dt>Prefix</dt><dd><code>{{keyPrefix}}</code></dd>
  <dt>Key</dt><dd><code class="api-key-secret">{{key}}</code></dd>
</dl>

<p>Use this key in the <code>Authorization: Bearer &lt;key&gt;</code> header of every request.</p>
